 When DMVs Cost Me My Job 
	 December 27, 2013 
	 by  SQLSoldier 
	 SQL Server 
	 31 Comments 
	 0 
 


 Help Wanted  Back in early 2006, I was still working at my first ever DBA job. I had only been a DBA for a little less than 3 years, but I felt like I knew a lot. I spent every night on the forums helping people with issues as a way of learning new things myself. But SQL Server 2005 was out and things were vastly different.
